vote.title: A resolution requesting the City of Dallas recognize the 15th of September as Park(ing) Day and request for the City Manager to begin planning and implementing actions to reduce parking in the city and provide briefings on the status of parking reduction and the elimination of minimum parking requirements in the city - Financing: No cost consideration to the City (via Councilmembers West, Bazaldua, Willis, Resendez, and Schultz)
